The Glenn Beck Radio Show OCT-28-2013 MON   PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program



          Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 10/28/13Monday, October 28, 2013 10:59 AM



Mike Rowe calls in to talk about the criticism he has received just for appearing on
  Glenn Beck's television show.

  Also, atheists on the left assume everyone who they like is an atheist as well.



  Plus, many popular Halloween costumes are banned at the University of Colorado.
